:   |   ::  []      : ---- Setting up Postbox ----
:   |   ::  []      : args example: ['args data example']
:   |   ::  []      : (Data is added in the *current* task, indexed by its *uuid*)
:   |   ::  []      : --------
:   |   ::  []      : UUID example: example::postbox[<uuid>] <- ['uuid data example']
:   |   ::  []      : (Data is added in the *target* task, indexed by *current* *uuid*)
:   |   ::  []      : --------
:   |   ::  []      : General Example 1: example::postbox    <- ['general data example']
:   |   ::  []      : General Example 2: example::postbox[-] <- ['general data example']
:   |   ::  []      : (Data is added to an implicit sub-box '-')
:   |   ::  []      : --------
:   |   ::  []      : Key Example 1: example::postbox[first]  <- ['blah', 'bloo', 'blee']
:   |   ::  []      : Key Example 2: example::postbox[second] <- ['aweg', 'qqqq']
:   |   ::  []      : (These target the same box, different index sub-box)
:   |   ::  []      : ----------------
:   |   ::  []      : ---- Crossing task boundaries ----
:   |   ::  []      : ----------------
:   |   ::  []      : Whole Previous Task Box Get example: example::_.add.data[*]
:   |   ::  []      : defaultdict(<class 'list'>, {UUID('f03ed2b5-7ec4-11f0-9bb5-1c834133728f'): ['args data example']})
:   |   ::  []      : --------
:   |   ::  []      : Whole Current Task Box Get example: example::postbox[*]
:   |   ::  []      : defaultdict(<class 'list'>, {UUID('f03ed2b5-7ec4-11f0-9bb5-1c834133728f'): ['uuid data example'], '-': ['general data example', 'general data example'], 'first': ['blah', 'bloo', 'blee'], 'second': ['aweg', 'qqqq']})
:   |   ::  []      : (The uuid mentioned here should be the same as in the previous task whole box example)
:   |   ::  []      : --------
:   |   ::  []      : Key Example 1: example::postbox[first]
:   |   ::  []      : ['blah', 'bloo', 'blee']
:   |   ::  []      : Key Example 2: example::postbox[second]
:   |   ::  []      : ['aweg', 'qqqq']
:   |   ::  []      : --------
:   |   ::  []      : No Key Example: example::postbox
:   |   ::  []      : ['general data example', 'general data example']
:   |   ::  []      : General Example: example::postbox[-]
:   |   ::  []      : ['general data example', 'general data example']
:   |   ::  []      : --------
